Image 3 of 3 showing our ray tracer handles falloff for point lights.

This image is of a green sphere with a specular component that reflects blue light.  There sphere is centered at the origin with a radius of 0.65.  It is under a white point light at (2,2,2) with quadratic falloff.  The rendered sphere is even less lit than the sphere created by input-12.  

Time to render: less than 1 second.

Command line:  ./as1 examples/input-13